HEADWORD: Kolarian
<hw>Ko*la"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld>
<def>An individual of one of the races of aboriginal inhabitants which
survive in Hindustan.</def> -- <def2><pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to the Kolarians.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

